    "en": {
      "title": "Sweden and Denmark ease travel advisories",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sweden and Denmark have taken steps to ease the travel advisories imposed on Sri Lanka. Both these countries relaxed their travel advisories yesterday evening which will be a positive sign for the revival of Sri Lanka's tourism sector.",
        "Currently, the tourism sector in Sri Lanka is gradually recovering and it will be a positive sign for the tourism sector in Sri Lanka."
